Solvent and Fragrance Room Spray 100 Ml
Greeting guests with a mist of fragrance is a traditional gracious hospitality. Room sprays are a quick and convenient way to give your home a delightful ambiance.
How to use
Shake gently hold upright towards the center of the room; press spray for desired amount. Be sure to avoid furniture when spraying.
Duration 1100 sprays
Where to use
Spray at entryway kitchen bedroom bathroom living room garden office restaurants/hotels & institutions.
